data.title: Inside Jesse James's extravagant wedding to Alexis DeJoria (but will it last with his FOURTH bride?)
data.meta_description: Sandra Bullock's ex-husband married Alexis Dejoria in a very extravagant and expensive affair in Malibu on Sunday.
data.text:
EXCLUSIVE Inside Jesse James's extravagant wedding to billionaire heiress Alexis DeJoria (but will it last with FOURTH bride?)

He's had a string of failed marriages, but that didn't stop Jesse James and his fourth bride from pulling out all the stops.

Sandra Bullock's ex-husband married Alexis Dejoria in a very extravagant and expensive affair in Malibu on Sunday.

However, it's hardly surprising that the serial cheat's wedding to the drag car racerwas a pricey affair.

Fourth time lucky? New pictures have emerged of Jesse James's fourth marriage to billionaire heiress Alexis DeJoria, which took place at her father Jon Paul DeJoria's Malibu estate over the weekend

After all her father is John Paul Dejoria, co-founder of the Paul Mitchell hair care products line and Patron Spirits Company.

In new aerial shots of the flashy nuptials, held at Jon Paul's sprawling Malibu property, Jesse is seen standing at an altar adorned with huge bouquets of pink, purple and white flowers.

Meanwhile, for her big day Alexis walked up the aisle wearing a traditional white dress adorned with a black embroidered floral design.

Sealed with a kiss: The former CEO of West Coast Choppers kissed his drag racing wife following the nuptials

One big happy family: Jesse and Alexis posed for pictures with her father Jon Paul and his wife Eloise Broady

The strapless attire featured a large train and also showed off her collection of arm tattoos.

The 35-year-old also donned a huge white veil, wore diamond drop earrings in her ears and carried a bouquet of lilac and white roses.

Meanwhile, Jesse was suited and booted in a black suit, white shirt and black tie.

At the altar: Jesse and Alexis exchanged vows at an extravagant altar featuring large lilac and white bouquets

Expensive bling: The pair reportedly placed expensive Neil Lane rings on each other's wedding fingers in front of the minister

Purple-themed: Alexis's bridesmaids wore strapless purple gowns

Alexis's bridesmaids carried on the purple theme by slipping into floor length strapless gowns featuring flowing silk skirts.

And her flower girls, Jesse's youngest daughter Sonny, nine, and Alexis' ten-year-old daughter Bella, also wore the colour lilac in the form of cute ruffled dresses.

During their vows, the couple exchanged Neil Lane rings in front of a minister.

Flowers girls: Jesse's youngest daughter Sonny, nine, left, and Alexis' ten-year-old daughter Bella, right, also wore the colour lilac to act as flower girls

Group shot: The whole bridal party posed for pictures following the ceremony

The two main men in her life: Alexis's father Jon Paul and her new husband helped her with her dress, a strapless black embroidered gown, as they made their way across the grass

Extravagant: Alexis also wore a dramatic long veil and carried a bouquet of purple and white roses

The nuptials were watched by numerous friends and family members, including the bride's father John Paul and his wife Eloise Broady, who also slipped into an extravagant embroidered gown.

And it appears that Jesse gets along famously with his in-laws, as he was seen cuddling up to them for happy snaps following the ceremony.

Jesse and Alexis also snuggled up together as they toasted their nuptials with several glasses of champagne.

And the notorious bad boy planted several kisses on his new wife as he wrapped his arm around her waist.

Step-father: Jesse was seen doting on his new wife's daughter Bella after the ceremony

Kiss me quick: The motorcycle and car enthusiast wraps his arm around his wife's waist and plants a kiss on her cheek

The couple tied the knot after only dating for around seven months.

It was rumoured that Jesse had the audacity to invite his ex-wife Sandra to the nuptials, despite the fact that the marriage ended due to his philandering ways.

It seems Jesse has colossal gall to match his colossal ego, a source told Star Magazine via RadarOnline. After all the hurt and humiliation hes caused her, Sandra is the last person on Earth who would attend that affair.

Even after their divorce, Jesse continued to get his digs in on Sandra, saying publicly that he felt empty inside during their marriage and sneering that he changed as a person after marrying some Hollywood actress. Sandra will never forget that.

Familiar scene? This is Jesse's fourth marriage after three failed unions

Cheers to us: Jesse, Alexis and her father and step mother enjoy a glass of bubbly following the nuptials

However the source went on to claim that Jesse has at times tried to 'reach out to her behind the scenes', and that perhaps the invite was intended as a 'peace offering'.

Their relationship imploded in 2010 after five years of marriage just days after Sandra's Oscar win for The Blind Side when she discovered he had been having an affair with a tattoo model.

But his choice in his new wife and the rush to make it to the altar has raised some suspicions as to Jesses motives.

Changed man? Jesse appears that he may have changed his ways and was attentive to his new wife throughout the ceremony

Lovely setting: The nuptials took place at Alexis's father's sprawling Malibu estate

In particular, the insider claims that Jesse has always had a man crush on Alexis billionaire father John Paul, who is co-founder of Paul Mitchell hair products, the Patron Spirits Company and the House Of Blues chain of nightclubs.

Alexis certainly looks his type: long dark hair, loves cars and tattoos. She also stands to inherit a great deal, as her father's fortune is said to be worth $4 billion.

The pair are said to have bonded over their mutual attraction to racing fast cars and were pictured together on September 23 during the Fall Nationals at the Texas Motorplex in Ennis, TX.

Pretty in purple: Sunny and Bella looked cute in their ruffled purple gowns

Surrounded: The couple were surrounded by several family members and friends as they exchanged their vows

The father of three remains on good terms with his first wife Karla James, the mother of two of his children, Chandler, 17, and Jesse Jr., 14, which can't be said of his second wife, porn star Janine Lindemulder, the mother of his daughter Sunny.

After a vicious court battle, Jesse won custody of Sunny in 2009 with Janine allowed weekly visitation rights during daytime hours.

Factors that contributed to the judge's decision was Janine's stint in jail and her addiction with prescription drugs.

Large: It appears that the occasion was a rather large affair considering the attendance

The judge was also motivated by the fact that Sunny's older siblings also live with James.

The West Coast Choppers CEO started dating tattoo artist Kat Von D in August 2010, shortly after his marriage to Sandra ended.

They announced their engagement in January 2011 and were set to wed later that year.

But the pair split for good that October, after which Kat branded Jesse a 'cheat.'

Getting ready for the wedding: Alexis and Jesse were pictured in Los Angeles just two days before their wedding day
